Misson Statement:
Our goal is to build a simple and clear prediction model using basic financial data and straightforward regression methods. 
By keeping the design easy to understand and reproduce, we ensure the team stays focused on accuracy, transparency, and learning. 
This project emphasizes using minimal tools and clean data to avoid unnecessary complexity. 
Success is measured by how well the model explains trends rather than how advanced it is.

Signed by: Anurag Ravi, Kevin Ngo, Yash Patel
